{"tid":925546,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有冇愛錯郎？】30億身家卓林冇得分 吳綺莉﹕唯一要理，是我女兒的感受","createTime":"2018-12-02T21:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T01:47:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce6bdc6aff48a158876ced457c3d9ba860e23826","tid":925546,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T21:57:20.000Z","msg":"成龍喺2015年4月推出首部中文版自傳《成龍：還沒長大就老了》，英文版亦將於後日（4日）全球發售，當中有唔少修訂。成龍自揭年輕時沉迷賭博和酒精，揮金如土同妓女玩樂。一直覺得太太林鳳嬌是貪圖錢財先同佢一齊，所以經常嗌交，仲出軌同吳綺莉搞婚外情。<br />\n不過，書中隻字不提成龍與吳綺莉嘅女兒吳卓林。被問到當年有冇愛錯人？吳綺莉今日以短訊回覆《蘋果》﹕「唯一我要理的，是我女兒的感受。」<br />\n成龍與吳綺莉在在99年2月傳出緋聞，當時成龍已有家室，二人矢口否認相戀，澄清只係兄妹。至同年10月，吳綺莉被傳出已經懷孕四個月，並曾親口承認腹中骨肉係成龍。吳綺莉其後誕下「小龍女」吳卓林，卓林今年已經19歲，早前更曾拍片尋父，更出櫃承認係同性戀者，但成龍喺活動上只冷淡回應﹕「如果她喜歡，那很好（If she likes it, that's fine）」。日前卓林與女友Andi結婚，成龍至今都係冇反應。<br />\n有指成龍身家至少30億港元，佢曾經講過遺產一半畀太太林鳳嬌同房祖名，剩下嘅就捐慈善，意即卓林可能連一分一毫都冇，唔少人因此抨擊成龍冷血無情，對女兒不聞不問。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181202/large/1543752028_c7f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181202%2Flarge%2F1543752028_c7f5.jpg&h=9c1ab12c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181202/58984392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58984392&d=Pic7oWfPPzNETeSzpWt5XE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=02bae0b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58984392&h=c82a8887\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181202/58984392</a>"},{"pid":"d9744e6b975ce9a9a76b79cb5a0db010faef427c","tid":925546,"uid":204222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T23:27:27.000Z","msg":"上一代情仇，下一代埋單"},{"pid":"451e1a33aac15f95a5ff6f65e92f8a86643e6ce9","tid":925546,"uid":198998,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T23:33:49.000Z","msg":"成蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9老母老豆害個女成世"},{"pid":"92f8b102d67b8998d08f101351640533ff912d44","tid":925546,"uid":79554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T23:55:21.000Z","msg":"出中即飛佼佼者"},{"pid":"4029a91366d87caa2dbdd4e04ae098f18a92e115","tid":925546,"uid":144275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:00:42.000Z","msg":"其實去到成龍呢個層次既演員都係得30億身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c847c0f0912273b300923c3aa22107fa0cff5084","tid":925546,"uid":17616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4029a91366d87caa2dbdd4e04ae098f18a92e115","tid":925546,"uid":144275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:00:42.000Z","msg":"其實去到成龍呢個層次既演員都係得30億身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:05:04.000Z","msg":"啲錢咁揚，睇下犯兵兵咩下場"},{"pid":"626cdc7efebe8d39d4657a16000927ff44d846d8","tid":925546,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:47:13.000Z","msg":"如果係仔既應該有得分<br />\n可惜"}]}